OTHELLO-PY
==========

Download all the files to some directory and then run as:

python othello_gui.py

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================

sudo apt-get install python-tk

# Installing edax engine
# Download latest engine from http://abulmo.perso.neuf.fr/edax/4.3/index.htm
# Following installation instructions from here https://github.com/johncheetham/othelloTk
# Using python3 with virtualenv virtualenv -p python3 envname
sudo apt-get install python3-tk
pip install othellotk

GAME INSTRUCTIONS
=================

Black is represented by -1 on the board
White is represented by 1 on the board
Empty is represented by 0 on the board
game.player() - Returns current player